sleep,you don't have to wake up,right?

03:07.270 --> 03:09.740
oh,god.Okay!

03:10.320 --> 03:12.120
wait for me!

03:12.130 --> 03:14.230
And you didn't see
frobisher in the nightclub?

03:14.240 --> 03:17.640
