looked like until the parking lot.

03:17.650 --> 03:18.990
No shit.You live in brooklyn,too?

03:19.000 --> 03:20.820
It's better in the the boroughs.

03:20.830 --> 03:21.950
I live in williamburg.

03:21.960 --> 03:24.010
Isn't that crazy?You come
all the way to florida and

03:24.020 --> 03:26.420
meet someone who
lives,like,five minutes away.

03:26.430 --> 03:29.670
