03:58.110 --> 03:59.980
you want me to keep going?

04:01.740 --> 04:05.710
We still don't have enough unless you
can identify the man who got in the limo.

04:08.830 --> 04:11.410
I only saw him for,like,a split second.

04:11.420 --> 04:13.630
Is there anything you can remember?

04:13.640 --> 04:16.940
Was he tall,short?Young,old?

04:16.950 --> 04:19.450
It was five years ago.

04:20.500 --> 04:24.570
