people you showed me from the government trial.

04:24.580 --> 04:26.490
And what about your one-night stand?

04:26.500 --> 04:29.300
Greg lived in
williamsburg.He was a waiter.

04:29.310 --> 04:31.290
He was staying in his friend's condo.

04:31.300 --> 04:35.340
Which we can't find because you don't
remember what part of town you were in.

04:35.350 --> 04:37.540
Why don't you try hypnosis?

04:38.360 --> 04:40.450
It helped me quit smoking.

04:40.820 --> 04:42.680
Still stuck in the parking lot?

04:42.690 --> 04:44.300
Afraid so.

04:46.660 --> 04:49.610
Well,you know what's going to happen
if we don't come up with anything?

04:49.620 --> 04:52.260
