- Ray...
- Yes,amos?

08:19.190 --> 08:22.980
You know how much mr.Frobisher's
case means to this firm.

08:24.040 --> 08:26.200
Get it done.

08:31.150 --> 08:33.120
Yes,sir.

08:33.940 --> 08:37.400
Roughly 5,200 employees
are involved in the suit.

08:37.840 --> 08:42.960
Arthur frobisher-- he wiped out
our whole retirement account.

08:43.280 --> 08:46.790
1.4 billion.Gone.

08:47.180 --> 08:51.200
So,you know,most of us,we
just lost everything we had.

08:51.210 --> 08:53.410
You have to stop torturing yourself.

08:56.030 --> 08:58.360
You're doing everything you can.

08:59.050 --> 09:00.230
Am I?

09:00.240 --> 09:02.500
Yes,katie,you are.

09:03.300 --> 09:06.520
Patty needs to know who got
in that limo with frobisher.

09:06.940 --> 09:10.770
And she keeps asking about
you-- my one-night stand.

09:10.780 --> 09:13.020
What if I can't keep this up?

09:14.640 --> 09:17.630
What if I slip,or they back
me into a corner or something?

09:17.640 --> 09:20.800
You're going to be fine.Okay?

09:24.370 --> 09:26.430
Maybe you should come in.

09:26.880 --> 09:30.290
- Why won't you just talk to them?
- And tell them what?

09:30.560 --> 09:32.840
I saw the same thing you did.

09:33.580 --> 09:36.990
Maybe you'd remember something
if you saw the pictures.

09:37.000 --> 09:42.800
Hey,if I go in there,then my wife
is going to find out about us,

09:42.810 --> 09:45.170
and then we'll be
over,and I don't want that.

09:45.180 --> 09:46.820
It's not about us.

09:46.830 --> 09:50.510
It's about frobisher and those
people whose lives he ruined.

09:51.410 --> 09:55.520
Patty is the only one holding
him responsible for this.

09:55.870 --> 09:59.330
You really think patty
hewes cares about you?

10:00.880 --> 10:03.840
Here is the complete
dossier on katie connor.

10:05.170 --> 10:06.660
Is she still seeing gregory?

10:06.670 --> 10:08.210
Almost every day.

10:09.380 --> 10:10.790
you think she knows anything?

10:12.130 --> 10:15.210
I'm not sure.Keep an eye on her.

10:15.430 --> 10:18.350
If she's going to give us something,she's
going to have to get it from him.

10:19.430 --> 10:25.360
My guy says he can get greg's stock
portfolio by the end of the week.

10:26.010 --> 10:27.140
Good.

10:27.150 --> 10:29.780
No.No,it's not good,patty.

10:30.000 --> 10:32.430
This kind of thing
could get me disbarred.

10:36.210 --> 10:38.220
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

10:39.280 --> 10:42.750
Are you still on the board of the
jazz society at lincoln center?

10:42.760 --> 10:44.000
Why?

10:44.690 --> 10:46.630
Well,the head of the
trilling school is on it,too,

10:46.640 --> 10:48.970
and I was wondering if you'd
put in a word in for megan...

10:48.980 --> 10:52.330
Tom,wake up.People think I fired you.

10:52.340 --> 10:54.520
Find another connection.

11:02.390 --> 11:03.880
What is it?

11:03.890 --> 11:05.620
I guess it's a rite of passage.

11:05.630 --> 11:08.400
- What is?
- It was the icu.

11:08.740 --> 11:12.880
I assisted on my first bypass yesterday,and
the patient's not doing so hot.

11:12.890 --> 11:14.610
Oh,baby,I'm sorry.

11:15.110 --> 11:17.290
The family looks at you like you're god.

11:17.850 --> 11:19.630
If they only knew...

11:26.930 --> 11:29.780
Shit.So much for exercise.

11:29.790 --> 11:31.260
What?

11:31.270 --> 11:33.010
What are you doing tonight?

11:33.020 --> 11:34.370
I got a couple hours.

11:34.380 --> 11:36.420
- So?
- Catch a movie?

11:36.430 --> 11:38.760
I'm in.Movie,tonight.

11:39.230 --> 11:41.010
You got your saxophone,sweetheart?

11:41.020 --> 11:43.660
I'm holding it.Daddy,I'm
going to be late for assembly.

11:43.690 --> 11:46.570
Okay,okay.You look bellisima.

11:46.580 --> 11:48.680
- Bye,dad.
- Bye-bye.

11:49.110 --> 11:52.620
Good luck with the solo.********

11:54.450 --> 11:56.800
You didn't tell me she was a musician.

11:56.810 --> 11:58.590
Martin,twice in one week.

11:58.600 --> 12:00.930
We got to stop meeting like this

12:00.940 --> 12:03.210
I was hoping we could
finish monday's chat.

12:04.650 --> 12:06.950
I appreciate the offer.

12:06.960 --> 12:10.690
I've been doing some soul searching--
I'm just not ready to start work yet.

12:11.030 --> 12:12.880
Bullshit.

12:15.620 --> 12:18.220
I know what's going on
between you and patty.

12:18.960 --> 12:20.640
Excuse me?

12:20.650 --> 12:22.500
The whole world sees it.

12:22.510 --> 12:26.170
She treats you like dirt for ten
years,won't share the spotlight,

12:26.180 --> 12:29.040
then she refuses to make you a partner.

12:29.910 --> 12:31.890
You don't know what you're
talking about,martin.

12:31.900 --> 12:33.110
Sure,I don'T.

12:33.120 --> 12:36.340
You're not a battered wife defending
