12:36.350 --> 12:37.260
Oh,geez.

12:37.270 --> 12:39.210
Yeah,that's it.No,you got it.That's me.

12:39.220 --> 12:41.800
You know,your little
girl-- she's terrific.

12:42.780 --> 12:44.940
She's the best thing
that's ever happened to me.

12:44.950 --> 12:46.960
She serious with the music?

12:47.380 --> 12:50.540
Yeah,she's pretty
serious,considering she's ten.

12:50.550 --> 12:53.140
I ask 'cause I know that she's
got an application at trilling.

12:56.940 --> 12:58.320
How do you know that?

12:58.330 --> 13:01.140
Well,I'm president elect
of the parents' board.

13:01.150 --> 13:03.930
You guys have put together
an outstanding app.

13:04.450 --> 13:07.470
Good,good.Megan's got
her heart set on trilling.

13:07.480 --> 13:09.120
All her friends are going.

13:09.130 --> 13:11.170
Got to say,it'S...

13:11.350 --> 13:15.800
it sure is tough though to accept an applicant
whose father checks the unemployed box.

13:18.770 --> 13:20.820
Martin...

13:21.160 --> 13:23.970
- don't do this.
- Come on,take it easy,tom.

13:24.180 --> 13:27.580
