of them even pretty good.

13:27.590 --> 13:30.920
But,at trilling,we've got the
music department in the entire city.

13:30.930 --> 13:33.130
Harvard,yale,princeton--

13:34.110 --> 13:36.510
without trilling,they
don't have orchestras.

13:37.810 --> 13:40.100
I'd love to see megan get in.

13:50.920 --> 13:52.470
Comedy or drama?

13:53.360 --> 13:54.810
I'm sorry?

13:55.250 --> 13:58.390
I heard you telling that other doctor
that you were going to go see a movie.

13:59.910 --> 14:03.620
Oh,I'm sorry you overheard
my personal conversation.

14:04.370 --> 14:06.290
Oh,I shouldn't have been listening.

14:08.080 --> 14:12.750
I want you to know that we are doing everything
that we can to make your grandfather comfortable.

14:12.760 --> 14:14.530
I know.Thanks.

14:14.540 --> 14:17.060
And I really appreciate all
the time you take with him.

14:17.610 --> 14:19.610
You've been great.

14:21.080 --> 14:24.490
So...comedy or drama?

14:26.400 --> 14:27.510
Uh,I don't know.

14:27.520 --> 14:32.080
I was thinking maybe the cassavetes
retrospective at film forum.

14:32.090 --> 14:34.930
I've never heard of that.Is it funny?

14:34.940 --> 14:37.490
No.It's pretty serious.

14:37.500 --> 14:38.980
'70s stuff.

14:38.990 --> 14:40.960
I guess I'm more the drama type.

14:40.970 --> 14:44.140
Oh,not me.I love comedies.You
know,they're just so funny.

14:44.150 --> 14:45.920
Oh,oh,check it out.

14:51.140 --> 14:55.250
My grandpa got me into
these old radio shows.Here.

14:58.560 --> 14:59.770
Who is this?

14:59.780 --> 15:01.350
It's jack benny.

15:03.450 --> 15:04.760
It's good.

15:06.190 --> 15:08.870
Grandpa loves the guy,so
i downloaded it for him.

15:09.180 --> 15:10.770
That'll be nice.

15:11.130 --> 15:13.270
Yeah.Well...

15:13.480 --> 15:15.360
enjoy your big night out.

15:15.750 --> 15:17.400
Thank you.

15:17.410 --> 15:20.370
And have some popcorn for
me.'Cause I'll be here.

15:20.380 --> 15:21.820
Sure thing.

15:23.620 --> 15:25.200
Oh,and dr.Conner...

15:26.370 --> 15:28.320
be a little naughty.

15:28.660 --> 15:30.910
Excuse me?

15:30.920 --> 15:33.130
Get something chocolate.

15:34.030 --> 15:36.540
You got it.

15:42.660 --> 15:43.900
Ellen?

15:43.910 --> 15:46.660
Hey,can you come in tomorrow?I
pulled more photos to run by you.

15:46.670 --> 15:49.070
Minor players,but we
should check them out.

15:49.080 --> 15:50.410
Okay,I can try.

15:50.420 --> 15:51.920
Cool.I'll be in the office at 8:00.

15:51.930 --> 15:53.690
