16:16.240 --> 16:18.980
They did this thing on frobisher's
broker during the criminal trial.

16:18.990 --> 16:20.860
And who is he?

16:21.010 --> 16:21.940
Katie...

16:21.950 --> 16:24.160
What's his name?

16:26.220 --> 16:29.020
- His name is luke richards.
- Luke richards?

16:29.030 --> 16:31.540
He was one of the broker's assistants.

16:31.790 --> 16:34.500
But ellen said all of
the assistants had alibis.

16:34.510 --> 16:37.360
Well,richards must be
lying,because I definitely saw him.

16:38.140 --> 16:42.020
Gregory,if you could have linked frobisher
to his broker,why didn't you tell me?

16:42.030 --> 16:43.530
Because I'm not going to get involved.

16:43.540 --> 16:44.790
What?Why not?

16:44.800 --> 16:46.830
I don't want to be another kato kalen.

16:46.840 --> 16:49.150
