ruin the rest of my life.

16:49.160 --> 16:50.550
- Gregory,for jes...
- No,no.

16:50.560 --> 16:53.490
Maybe I'm an asshole,but I'm not going to
let these people use me and throw me away.

16:53.500 --> 16:54.940
Which is exactly what
they're going to do.

16:54.950 --> 16:57.370
Okay,well,forget about
them.What about me?

16:57.380 --> 17:01.410
I have risked everything I have to put
this guy away,and now you're just going...

17:01.420 --> 17:03.540
Going to be a selfish prick?Yeah.

17:03.550 --> 17:05.210
And you should,too.

17:05.980 --> 17:07.690
Think about it,katie.

17:07.700 --> 17:12.849
You're going to lose your restaurant,your
privacy,any shot at having a normal life.

17:13.579 --> 17:16.089
I do care about you.

17:16.780 --> 17:19.369
I don't want to see you get hurt.

17:19.740 --> 17:21.890
Stay out of it.

17:22.329 --> 17:25.829
Just stay out of it,okay?

17:28.580 --> 17:29.990
Katie...

17:53.340 --> 17:55.950
Darrell goldstein interned
at frobisher's company.

17:55.960 --> 17:57.170
No,not him.

17:57.180 --> 17:59.430
- Paul ordell-- he
was a temp. - No.

18:00.640 --> 18:02.950
Luke richards.

18:08.090 --> 18:10.470
Katie,what is it?

18:11.720 --> 18:14.290
Hi,there.I'm arthur.

18:14.300 --> 18:15.940
Oh,my god.

18:16.880 --> 18:18.400
Katie?

18:18.410 --> 18:20.420
You want me to be a
witness against frobisher?

18:20.430 --> 18:21.860
Yes,if you know something.

18:21.870 --> 18:25.340
She's going to be screwed.She
will lose everything,won't she?

18:32.070 --> 18:34.230
Nothing.Keep going.

18:35.060 --> 18:36.690
Stephen gilbride.

18:38.070 --> 18:39.620
No,not him.

18:41.580 --> 18:43.410
Jason raber.

18:43.850 --> 18:45.680
No,not him.

18:46.010 --> 18:50.570
You and I,we never really spoke
when we were down in florida,did we?

18:51.150 --> 18:53.070
No,no,that's right.

18:53.680 --> 18:57.180
I want the straight story,and until
you tell me,you're worthless to me.

18:57.190 --> 18:59.560
I don't give a shit about you.

19:02.560 --> 19:04.540
No,go back to that other guy.

19:05.170 --> 19:07.990
No,before him.Yeah,him.

19:10.530 --> 19:12.910
You recognize him?

19:13.610 --> 19:15.260
When was this picture taken?

19:15.270 --> 19:17.490
Last year.Why?

19:19.090 --> 19:21.970
